    bindsym h resize grow width 1 px or 1 ppt, move container left 1 px

    bindsym Mod1+l resize shrink width 20 px or 20 ppt, move container right 20 px
    bindsym Mod1+k resize grow height 20 px or 20 ppt, move container up 20 px
